title: Lots of cleanup.
message:
Lots of cleanup.

 - Remove dependency on ActionBarSherlock.
 - Upgrade the target SDK version to 21.
 - Use the appcompat theme for material design.

title: Finish migration to ActionBarSherlock.
message:
Finish migration to ActionBarSherlock.

Every activity should now show an action bar with which one should
be able to navigate.

* Add Tab navigation to main view, not finished.
* Remove unnecessarily duplicated resources.

title: Reformat everything. ActionBarSherlock.
message:
Reformat everything. ActionBarSherlock.

* Let IntelliJ reformat all of the Java code.
* Add ActionBarSherlock to be able to use an action bar on older Android
  versions.
* Replace the custom bar on the main view with an action bar from
  ActionBarSherlock.
* Add search and the menu to the action bar.
